{"word":"G1653 - ἐλεέω - eleéō - el-eh-eh'-o - Have compassion","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐλεέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eleéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">el-eh-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Have compassion</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இரக்கம்பெறு, இரங்கு, இரக்கமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to have mercy on"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1656 - ἔλεος - éleos - el'-eh-os/1656\">G1656</a>; to <i>compassionate</i> (by word or deed, specifically by divine grace): - have compassion (pity on), have (obtain, receive, shew) mercy (on).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1653/1653\">G1653</a>, <a href=\"#/G1654/1654\">G1654</a>, <a href=\"#/G1655/1655\">G1655</a>, <a href=\"#/G1656/1656\">G1656</a>, <a href=\"#/G415/415\">G415</a>, <a href=\"#/G448/448\">G448</a>"}]}